102
00:06:06,541 --> 00:06:07,791
Hmmm.

103
00:06:07,875 --> 00:06:10,041
Tell you what, I'm going
to let you take a shot

104
00:06:10,125 --> 00:06:13,291
at them first. I'll be
standing by if you need me.

105
00:06:13,375 --> 00:06:15,125
[MILLIANNA]
Hey, wait! All alone?

106
00:06:15,208 --> 00:06:17,125
[KAGURA] You need to
gain more experience.

107
00:06:17,208 --> 00:06:20,000
This is your opportunity
to show me what you can do.

108
00:06:20,083 --> 00:06:23,250
Don't treat it like a game,
it's a serious fight.

109
00:06:23,333 --> 00:06:25,000
[KAGURA] Don't let
me down, Millianna.

110
00:06:25,083 --> 00:06:28,208
[MILLIANNA] I won't!
I'll beat 'em, you just watch!

111
00:06:28,291 --> 00:06:30,833
We can't get lazy just because
they're girls, ya hear?

112
00:06:30,916 --> 00:06:32,000
They're tough so
we need to give it

113
00:06:32,083 --> 00:06:33,833
everything we've
got in this battle.

114
00:06:33,916 --> 00:06:37,541
Especially if we want
to beat Kagura. That's it!

115
00:06:37,625 --> 00:06:40,125
[LYON] If I claim
victory for Lamia Scale...

116
00:06:41,458 --> 00:06:43,500
then Juvia will
fall in love with me!

117
00:06:43,583 --> 00:06:46,416
[YUKA] Aw, geez. Get your
priorities straight, man.

118
00:06:46,500 --> 00:06:48,875
'Kay boys! You'd better
kick some butt this round

119
00:06:48,958 --> 00:06:50,791
or I'll take ya
both for a spin!

120
00:06:50,875 --> 00:06:54,208
[MATO] Remember you've only got
thirty minutes to seal the deal!

121
00:06:54,291 --> 00:06:57,500
Now, let the match begin!

122
00:06:57,583 --> 00:06:59,833
[MILLIANNA]
If you snooze, you lose!

123
00:07:01,291 --> 00:07:03,583
Bad Kitty Restraint Tube!

124
00:07:07,000 --> 00:07:09,583
[BETH] Whoa, is Millianna
gonna fight 'em all by herself?

125
00:07:09,666 --> 00:07:11,041
I don't think she's
ready to take on

126
00:07:11,125 --> 00:07:12,750
Lamia Scale on her own.

127
00:07:12,833 --> 00:07:15,833
Well, Kagura seems to think
that she can handle it.

128
00:07:15,916 --> 00:07:17,833
[LISLIE] Let's just
hope she's right.

129
00:07:19,375 --> 00:07:22,125
I don't need any help
with these guys! Ha!

130
00:07:23,500 --> 00:07:26,083
