if she beats both of them.

131
00:07:26,166 --> 00:07:28,416
We'll be the laughing
stock of the tournament.

132
00:07:28,500 --> 00:07:32,458
[OHBA] I don't know what
you're up to, Mermaid Heel...

133
00:07:32,541 --> 00:07:34,416
but we're not gonna
let you get away with it!

134
00:07:34,500 --> 00:07:37,458
Go get 'em, Lyon and Yuka!
