135
00:07:37,541 --> 00:07:40,083
when you mess
with Laymia Scale!

136
00:07:40,166 --> 00:07:42,083
Hey, why's Kagura
just standing there?

137
00:07:42,166 --> 00:07:44,583
Good question. Bet I
can get her to fight.

138
00:07:44,666 --> 00:07:47,083
[LYON] Ice Make Eagle!

139
00:07:50,666 --> 00:07:52,666
I'm your opponent, not her!

140
00:07:53,750 --> 00:07:55,125
Wave!

141
00:07:58,125 --> 00:07:59,458
Holy!

142
00:07:59,541 --> 00:08:01,916
[MILLIANNA] Kitten Blaster!

143
