144
00:08:06,125 --> 00:08:07,625
[MILLIANNA] I've got you now!

145
00:08:07,708 --> 00:08:09,708
Kitty Punch! Kitty Punch!
Kitty Punch! Kitty Punch!

146
00:08:09,791 --> 00:08:11,750
Man, That's gotta hurt!
Who would've thought

147
00:08:11,833 --> 00:08:14,375
such a cute, little cat-girl
could be so incredibly vicious?

148
00:08:14,458 --> 00:08:16,250
Whoa, that's one
hard-core kitty!

149
00:08:16,333 --> 00:08:18,625
She's definitely not
holding back in this fight.

150
00:08:18,708 --> 00:08:20,458
She must feel more
confident knowing that

151
00:08:20,541 --> 00:08:22,250
Kagura's there
if she needs her.

152
00:08:24,166 --> 00:08:25,208
[MILLIANNA]
What's the matter, boys?

153
00:08:25,291 --> 00:08:27,000
You're not scared, are you?

154
00:08:27,083 --> 00:08:28,416
Then again, maybe you should be

155
00:08:28,500 --> 00:08:30,791
'cause I've been
training with Kagura daily!

156
00:08:32,583 --> 00:08:34,000
[MILLIANNA] Special technique.

157
00:08:35,416 --> 00:08:37,416
